{"tid":2316980,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★教仔？】地監局：希望代理不要打架，認為管理層亦要負責","createTime":"2020-12-08T08:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T09:54:06.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c5c521eb4c02aa1036fde8ad0eea1a33c79cc22b","tid":2316980,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T08:51:42.000Z","msg":"地監局主席廖玉玲表示，疫情下會做更多網上巡查，發現違規情況包括放盤未獲業主同意，及資料準確性等問題。<br />\n<br />\n另外，她提到回佣問題複雜，涉及法律、經營手法問題等，亦包括對公眾資訊保障問題，但強調不會與代理鬧僵，認為溝通重要，又指<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>希望代理不要打架</strong></span>，認為管理層亦要負責，要制定有效措施防止員工相關行為，難以直接指明有關公司要如何做，要視乎個案而定，她未正面回應會否向公司或管理層除牌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564219-20201208.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564219-20201208.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7EcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=db2ee318\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564219-20201208.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=61e784cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564219-20201208.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"21103371564aba2aea3ba91839ab61e460744d24","tid":2316980,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T08:51:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7228f8a391f8a98d196c9bf31a4f459480b19a0b","tid":2316980,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T08:52:13.000Z","msg":"AA狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57af1776c840ed5f04435ae6e0ce167a7f9f1d4d","tid":2316980,"uid":114